{
  "texts": [
    "To address this, we chose to treat all identified themes under a term, \"suggested RAI practices.\"",
    "This approach allows us to present a comprehensive view of the current discussions on RAI without imposing distinctions that were not clear in the primary sources, while also aligning with our research question.",
    "Extracted informationWhen reviewing, we learned that both users and non-users could be stakeholders of suggested RAI practices.",
    "Users directly interacted with the AI-enabled systems.",
    "Non-users did not directly interact with the AI-enabled system but were directly involved in the development, deployment, use, or management of the AI-enabled system."
  ]
}